title: Full day PRIVATE to Paracas, Ica and Huacachina from Lima All Inclusive and Lunch
description: Maximize your precious vacation time in Peru and experience the best of Paracas, Icas, and Huacachina on a private day tour from Lima. After transfer to Paracas, take a yacht tour to the Ballestas Islands to see penguins and sea lions. Taste wines and pisco sours at a vineyard in El Catador, then enjoy lunch at a traditional restaurant (vegetarian option available). Take pictures at the Huacachina Oasis before riding a sandboard down the dunes.
all_descriptions: Maximize your precious vacation time in Peru and experience the best of Paracas, Icas, and Huacachina on a private day tour from Lima. After transfer to Paracas, take a yacht tour to the Ballestas Islands to see penguins and sea lions. Taste wines and pisco sours at a vineyard in El Catador, then enjoy lunch at a traditional restaurant (vegetarian option available). Take pictures at the Huacachina Oasis before riding a sandboard down the dunes.

ItineraryThis is a typical itinerary for this productStop At:Paracas, Paracas, Ica RegionPassengers board the boat to go to the Ballestas Islands (Important: For security reasons the yacht cannot go with less than 15 people since it has a minimum weight for its better stability, if there were fewer people than the minimum capacity it is shared with other passengers, in conclusion this is the only part that would be shared for a safety reason for our passengers.Duration: 2 hoursStop At:Ica, Ica, Ica RegionVisit to the winery to do wine tasting and Pisco tasting.Duration: 1 hourStop At:Ica, Ica, Ica RegionLunch included in the Catador Restaurant; Includes: Entrance, main course, soft drink and pisco toast.Duration: 1 hourStop At:Huacachina, Huacachina, Ica Regionvisit to the huacachina oasis, moment of photographs to know the legend that of the lagoon and you can take time to shop.Duration: 30 minutesStop At:Ica Region, Ica RegionTubular, bugouis and sandboarding, at which point the tubular vehicles are boarded and they take a tour through the desert of the dunes, of pure adrenalineDuration: 1 hour

Private Fullday Paracas-Ica

⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️

Our private tour with Diana and Carlos was absolutely fantastic! Diana's knowledge of the history and current events in Paracas, Ica, and Huacachina was impressive. She shared so much fascinating information throughout the tour, making our experience incredibly enriching.

Diana was also incredibly patient and accommodating with our schedule at each stop, ensuring we had enough time to explore and enjoy each location to the fullest.

Carlos, our driver, was outstanding! His skills behind the wheel were top-notch, and we always felt safe on the road. His efficiency meant we got back to our hotel before 7 pm, which was perfect for us.

If you prefer having control over your itinerary, booking a private tour is a must. Request Diana and Carlos. Gracias, Carlos y Diana, for an unforgettable day!
